What I can't figure out - is there are two seals. Here is a link to
something like what I bought -

http://www.amazon.com/Flaming-River-FR1002-Battery-Disconnect/dp/B000HM579K/
ref=sr_1_9?ie=UTF8
<http://www.amazon.com/Flaming-River-FR1002-Battery-Disconnect/dp/B000HM579K
